## ExecutionSession methods

The `ExecutionSession` object has all sandbox methods bound to the specific session:

| Category             | Methods                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
| -------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
